text: Mahomet may refer to: ==People== *Muhammad (in Medieval Latin or French) *Sake Dean Mahomet, an 18th-century Bengali traveler *Mahomet Weyonomon, a Native American tribal chieftain of the Mohegan tribe from Connecticut ==Other uses== *Mahomet (play), by Voltaire *Mahomet, Illinois, a village in the United States
title: Mahomet
